# Profile show — matchmaking (mediator) placement

- Do **not** render the matchmaking / mediator request button (`matrimony.profile.mediator-request`, `contact_access.mediator_submit`, `show_mediator_cta`) inside the hero **ACTIONS** `<aside>` on `matrimony/profile/show.blade.php`.
- The **only** product location for that CTA is the Contact Information section via `resources/views/matrimony/profile/partials/contact-mediator-cta.blade.php` (included next to locked / gated contact states).
- If you need to change matchmaking UX, edit the partial or contact-section includes — never duplicate the control in the actions rail.
